description:
This is an implementation issue for the CI dropdown in the pipeline editor ~backend 

1. `TemplateType` for the following query, with the the `name` and `id` field. 

```
query ciTemplatesList($projectPath: ID!) {
  templates {
    name
    id
  }
}
```

2. `TemplatesResolver` that takes an ID and returns the content:  

```
query ciTemplatesContent($projectPath: ID!, $templateID: ID!) {
  templates(id: $templateID) {
    content
  }
}
```

### Related issues

~frontend issue https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/299430
